    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This RFC gives a description of what the Hostnames Server is and how to access it.  The function of this particular server is to deliver machine-readable name/address information describing networks, gateways, hosts, and eventually domains, within the internet environment.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
